						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Sadāśiva. Śaka 1467 = A.D. 1545.</hi></p>						

						<p>Remission of taxes from the village of Kūvam <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Narasānāyakkarpuram, in Kaṉṟūr-nāḍu, a subdivision of Teṉkarai Maṇaviṟkōṭṭam in the Chandragiri-rājyam in favour of the Narasiṅgaperumāḷ temple by Saṅkaranāyakkar [Li]ṅganāyakar for the merit of Chinna Timmayadēva Mahārāja, son of Irāmarāsa Timmaya. The taxes exempted are <hi rend="italic">makamai, suṅgam</hi> and <hi rend="italic">āḷ-amañji.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
